Description: Windows-like middle-click autoscroll for X11
 Activates smooth autoscroll when the middle mouse button is held.
 Releasing the button immediately cancels scrolling so that normal
 middle-click behaviour is preserved for short presses.
 .
 An anchor overlay and directional indicator are displayed while
 autoscroll is active.
